    "Name": "Xanthos",
    "Details": "A Republic era model, this version uses a 400XL fusion engine to reach a top speed of 64 km/h. It is protected by standard armor and CASE II in case the two Clan-spec Gauss Rifles explode. The Gauss Rifles are supported by four Clan-built ER Medium Lasers.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Quad Mech</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.18</color></b>",
